50:11.641 --> 50:12.983
Come to these sessions tomorrow.

50:13.724 --> 50:15.586
I want you to come hungry.

50:16.647 --> 50:19.250
Come thirsty for God.

50:20.162 --> 50:27.092
and in our joy, in our satisfaction, in our delight in Him, embattled as it is in this life, dynamic as it is in this life.

50:27.473 --> 50:28.394
He is honored.

50:28.655 --> 50:29.656
He's exalted.

50:30.057 --> 50:35.585
He's glorified because God is most glorified in us when we are most satisfied in Him.

50:36.567 --> 50:38.810
Let's pray.

50:38.830 --> 50:49.426
So Father in Heaven, for everyone in the room, would you be pleased by the quiet fire

50:49.634 --> 51:03.828
of your Holy Spirit to impart real joy to your people, through your word, by your spirit, in the fellowship of those who love and cherish and delight in Jesus.

51:04.469 --> 51:17.522
Would you be pleased this weekend to deepen, strengthen, give real joy in the soul that satisfies our greatest longings, albeit imperfectly in this life?

51:18.562 --> 51:27.566
and that makes a name for you in our home, in our neighborhood, in our church, in our cities, in our nations, in this world.

51:28.408 --> 51:29.390
In Jesus' name we pray.

51:30.373 --> 51:30.834
Amen.

